     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <pb facs="2"/>
   <head>To the Louing Reider</head>
   <lg>
      <l>GIf pacience, vith confidence, of God hes had reuaird,</l>
      <l>Gif reuerence, obedience, be giftis not a bill</l>
      <l>Vith reason, but treason, humilitie be stabil</l>
      <l>To Catholik, Apostolik, the victor is de-claird.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>Gif periurie, and traitorie, be vyces venemous,</l>
      <l>Gif sclander, can rander, his maister recompance</l>
      <l>The Protestant so molestant, be al intelligence,</l>
      <l>For hyi re, the fyi-re sal get of Cerberus.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <salute>Adieu.</salute>
   </closer>
</div>
